sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App Code
    participant HUD as HUD
    participant GT as Grace Timer
    participant MST as MinShow Timer
    participant UI as UI Display

    Note over App,UI: Scenario 1: Fast task (< graceTime) — HUD never shown

    App->>HUD: show()
    activate HUD
    HUD->>GT: Start graceTimer (0.5s)
    App->>HUD: hide() (after 0.3s)
    HUD->>GT: Cancel graceTimer
    HUD->>HUD: removeFromSuperview()
    deactivate HUD
    Note over UI: User sees nothing

    Note over App,UI: Scenario 2: Slow task (> graceTime) — HUD shown with minShowTime

    App->>HUD: show()
    activate HUD
    HUD->>GT: Start graceTimer (0.5s)
    GT-->>HUD: Timer fired (0.5s elapsed)
    HUD->>UI: Display HUD
    activate UI
    HUD->>MST: Start minShowTimer (1.0s)
    App->>HUD: hide() (after 0.7s, only 0.2s visible)
    Note over MST: minShowTime not met yet
    MST-->>HUD: Timer fired (1.0s total display)
    HUD->>UI: Hide HUD
    deactivate UI
    HUD->>HUD: removeFromSuperview()
    deactivate HUD
